OL,3,CSurviving, not living: The workers
OL,4,Ctaking second jobs in cost-of-living
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FWhether it's employees or employers,
OL,8,Fthe last two years have been the
OL,9,Ftoughest in living memory, ITV News
OL,10,FInvestigations Editor Dan Hewitt
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FJamie is knackered. The builder sits
OL,14,Fslumped on his sofa, in his one
OL,15,Fbedroom flat in Bridgend, having
OL,16,Ffinished a hard day on the tools.
OL,18,FIt's 7pm. The 35-year-old looks
OL,19,Fmentally as well physically exhausted,
OL,20,Fbut his working day is not yet done.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
