OL,3,CSurviving, not living: The workers
OL,4,Ctaking second jobs in cost-of-living
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,F"It's just, you can work all the hours
OL,8,Fyou want, but it's just not enough. So
OL,9,Fthe second income was sort of a needs
OL,10,Fmust."
OL,12,FI arrived at Jamie's at the start of
OL,13,Fthe day, just after 5.30am.
OL,15,FHe was up before the sun, and his
OL,16,Fworking day won't end until after it
OL,17,Fhas set.
OL,19,FEvery hour counts, because so does
OL,20,Fevery penny.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
