OL,7,FI ask Jamie how long he plans to do
OL,8,Fthis for.
OL,10,F"I've burned out before, and you kind
OL,11,Fof do feel just drained, mentally
OL,12,Fexhausted... You need a timeout, but
OL,13,Fbills don't take a timeout.
OL,15,F"It's a week-to-week paycheck. I don't
OL,16,Fknow. I honestly don't know."
