OL,4,Ctaking second jobs in cost-of-living
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FFull time workers in Wales are on
OL,8,Faverage #42 per week worse off in real
OL,9,Fterms than they were three years ago,
OL,10,Faccording to the Office for National
OL,11,FStatistics (ONS).
OL,13,FNearly a third of households (28%)
OL,14,Ftold the Bevan Foundation they've had
OL,15,Fto borrow money to survive in the last
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,18,FA few miles away, still in Bridgend,
OL,19,Fin one of South Wales' beautiful
OL,20,Fvalleys, live Rob and Robyn.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/20
