OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FThey have three children. The
OL,8,Fyoungest, Imogen, arrived four weeks
OL,9,Fago. She was a wonderful surprise to
OL,10,Ftwo working parents whose other
OL,11,Fchildren are 13 and nine years old.
OL,13,FThey have been further shocked by the
OL,14,Fcosts that have followed.
OL,16,FWe join Robyn picking up baby supplies
OL,17,Fin her local supermarket.
OL,19,F"Formula, #14.45 - it's quite a lot -
OL,20,FI remember it being #9 when my (elder)
OL,21,Fdaughter was a baby," she says.
