OL,7,F"It is quite a worry because
OL,8,Feverything is going up... You know it
OL,9,Fdoesn't cost that much to make, but
OL,10,Fobviously it's profit for the
OL,11,Fcompanies.
OL,13,F"Nappies, new baby ones, they're #9.
OL,14,FSo she's gone through #36 of nappies
OL,15,Fsince she's been born.
OL,17,F"When she gets into the food stuff, I
OL,18,Fwill make it otherwise you're looking
OL,19,Fat #2 a meal."
