OL,7,FBack at their three bedroom home,
OL,8,Fwhich they rent from a housing
OL,9,Fassociation, her husband Rob is
OL,10,Fpreparing to go to work. He's a
OL,11,Fdelivery driver for a supermarket, and
OL,12,Falso plays darts, which sometimes
OL,13,Fbrings in an extra bit of cash.
OL,15,FThey struggled even before Imogen was
OL,16,Fborn.
OL,18,FRob's wages won't be enough by the
OL,19,Ftime Robyn's maternity pay ends, the
OL,20,Fcouple explains
