OL,4,Ctaking second jobs in cost-of-living
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,F"Over the years where we have
OL,8,Fstruggled. We've lent money, payday
OL,9,Floans etcetera," says Rob.
OL,11,F"Money comes in, it goes out, and no
OL,12,Fmatter how much money there is, you
OL,13,Falways find something that needs to be
OL,14,Fdone."
OL,16,F"Basically everything, the monthly
OL,17,Fdirect debits, the bigger bills like
OL,18,Fthe rent, the council tax, the car
OL,19,Finsurance, the car finance... that's
OL,20,Fgone off up," says Robyn.
