OL,7,F"It's ridiculous."
OL,9,FThe biggest dilemma ahead for the
OL,10,Fcouple is when, if, Robyn goes back to
OL,11,Fwork as an occupational therapist in
OL,12,Fthe NHS after maternity leave.
OL,14,FThey need her wage to get by, but the
OL,15,Fcost of nursery fees - which would be
OL,16,Fwell over #1,000 a month if she
OL,17,Freturned full time - has her
OL,18,Fquestioning what's best.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/20
