OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FEmployment in Wales is the lowest of
OL,8,Fthe four nations of the UK. It also
OL,9,Fhas the most people classed as
OL,10,Feconomically inactive.
OL,12,FFor Welsh businesses, desperate to
OL,13,Fgrow and hire more people, there's a
OL,14,Ffear things are going backwards.
OL,16,FA short drive across to the capital
OL,17,Ffrom Bridgend, we visit Cardiff
OL,18,FGalvanisers, a family-run business
OL,19,Fthat has been brought to its knees by
OL,20,Frising outgoings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/20
