OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FAt a giant metal processing plant,
OL,8,Fwhere they predominantly supply
OL,9,Fproducts for the housing industry, 18
OL,10,Fmonths ago their annual energy bill
OL,11,Fjumped from #280,000 to #1.2 million.
OL,13,FTheir energy bill has since dropped to
OL,14,F#600,000, but having survived that
OL,15,Fenormous jump, they are now facing a
OL,16,Fslowdown in work and jobs are under
OL,17,Fthreat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/20
